cars.description: Renting my beauty. Well looked after always clean come and pick it up.
Step into the future with our beautiful electric four-door fastback sedan.
Fast, small and nimble. You know what the logo means, its mercedes.
This is a true sports car over here, no joke. Comes with a beautiful engine, interior.
Can you ever not want a supercar? Its everyone's dream. You will remember it.
Small and easy to park, cheap on fuel loads of fun.
Quite a good city and highway car. If you have a family it has plenty of space.
It is the best of France, good looks and beautiful driving experience.
Its the utimate do everything car. Dads and families love it.
Car is perfect, big so you do not worry about cerbs. Bunch of space inside i love it.
